query:
INSERT INTO
    weather_images (
        "timestamp",
        wind_speed_10m,
        air_temperature_2m,
        relative_humidity_2m,
        air_pressure_at_sea_level,
        precipitation_amount
    )
VALUES
    (
        $1::TIMESTAMPTZ,
        $2::BYTEA,
        $3::BYTEA,
        $4::BYTEA,
        $5::BYTEA,
        $6::BYTEA
    )
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
